{{notability|date=May 2018}} {{Infobox museum | name = Duplex Art Gallery | native_name = | native_name_lang = | image = | imagesize = | caption = | alt = | map_type = | map_caption = | map_alt = | coordinates = {{coord|43|52|N|18|25|E|region:BA|display=inline,title}} | established = 2004 | dissolved = | location = [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]] | type = [[Art gallery]] | collection = 3,000 | visitors = | director = Pierre Courtin | president = | curator = | publictransit = | network = | website = [http://www.duplex100m2.com/ www.duplex100m2.com] }} The '''Duplex Art Gallery''' is a private [[art gallery]] in [[Sarajevo]], [[Bosnia and Herzegovina]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiosarajevo.ba/metromahala/kultura/otvorena-nova-galerija-duplex-u-100m2/85152|title=Otvorena nova Galerija Duplex u 100m2|publisher=radiosarajevo.ba}}</ref> It was established in 2004 by French artist Pierre Courtin.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sff.ba/stranica/pierre-courtin|title=Pierre Courtin|publisher=sff.ba}}</ref> The twin galleries Galerija10m2 and Duplex100m2, that are run under the Duplex banner, have organized more than 200 exhibitions in Sarajevo and over 25 multimedia projects in [[Belgrade]], [[Zagreb]], [[Paris]], [[Budapest]], [[Athens]], [[New Orleans]], [[New York City|New York]], [[Vienna]], [[Lyon]], [[Stockholm]] and [[Montreal]].<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.radiosarajevo.ba/metromahala/kultura/kupujmo-domace-najbolji-domaci-autori-u-galeriji-duplex/231153|title=Izložba/ Kupujmo domaće: Najbolji domaći autori u galeriji Duplex|publisher=radiosarajevo.ba}}</ref> ==References== {{Reflist}}
